sentences: Nagi Jamal Omar (born 16 December 1986 in Tumba), better known as simply Nano, is a Swedish singer and songwriter.
He first came to prominence while competing in Melodifestivalen 2017.
Omar was born on 16 December 1986 in Tumba, Botkyrka, Stockholm.
At age 12, he moved to a foster home in Gotland.
He currently lives with his partner and four children in Södertälje.
